hadiths[117]{hadithnumber,text}:
1205,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''halal wazeh hai aur haram bhi wazeh hai aur uskey darmiyan bahut si cheezen shubha wali hain padhi. jinhen bahut sey log nahin jantey hain ke ye halal key qabeel sey hain ya haram key, to jisney apney Deen ko pak karney aur apni izzat bachaney key liye unhen chhodey rakha to wo maamoon raha aur jo un mein sey kisi mein pad gaya yani unhen ikhtiyar kar liya to qarib hai ke wo haram mein mubtala ho jaey, jaisey wo shakhs jo sarkari charaagaah key qarib ( apna janwer ( churaa raha ho, qarib hai ke wo is mein waqey ho jaey, jaan lo ke har badshah ki eik charaagaah hoti hai aur Allah ki charaagaah uski haram karda cheezen hain''. dusri sanad sey muallif ney Shaaby sey aur unhoney ney Noman bin Bashir Raziallahu anhuma sey isi tarah ki usi mafhoom ki hadees riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, usey kaee riwayaton ney Shaaby sey aur Shaaby ney Noman bin Bashir sey riwayat kya hai."
1206,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sood leney waley, sood deney waley, uskey dono gawahon aur uskey likhney waley par lanat bheji hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umar, Ali, Jabir aur abu-Juhaifa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1207,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kabeera gunahon padhi. sey mutalliq farmaya : '' Allah key sath shirk karna , waliden ki nafarmani karna, kisi ko) nahaq ( qatl karna aur jhooti baat kehna (badey gunahon mein sey hain). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai 2- is bab mein abu-Bakra, aiman bin Khurem aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1208,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey paas tashrif laye, hum (us waqt ( « سماسرہ  ( dalaal ( kahlaatey they, aap ney farmaya : '' aey taajiron ki jamaat ! kharid o farokht key waqt shetan aur gunah sey sabiqa pad hi jata hai, lihaza tum apni kharid farokht ko sadqa key sath mila liya karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Qais bin abi Ghaza ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey mansoor ney basanad « Aamash w Habib bin abi Sabit», padhi. aur deegar kaee logon ney basanad «abi Wayl an Qais bin abi Gharza» sey riwayat kya hai. hum uskey ilawa Qais ki koi aur hadees nahin jantey jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho, 3- muallif ney basanad أبو معاوية an الأعمش an شقيق بن سلمة وشقيق هو أبو Waeyl an Qais بن أبي غرزة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم isi jaisi isi mafhoom ki hadees riwayat ki hai, 4- ye hadees sahih hai, 5- is bab mein Bara bin Aazib aur Rifaa sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1209,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sacha aur amanat daar taajir ( qiyamat key din ( anbiya , siddiqeen aur shohda key sath hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, hum usey ba-riwayat Sory sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain unhoney abu-Hamza sey riwayat ki hai, 2- aur abu-Hamza ka naam Abdullah bin Jabir hai aur wo Basra key Shekh hain."
1210,"wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eid gaah ki taraf nikley, aap ney logon ko kharid-o-farokht kartey dekha to farmaya : '' aey tajiron ki jamaat! ''to log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baat sunney lagey aur unhoney aap ki taraf apni gardanen aur nigahen oonchi kar lin, aap ney farmaya : ''taajir log qiyamat key din gunehgar uthaey jaeyngey siwaye uskey jo Allah sey darey nek kaam karey aur sach boley''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Ismail bin Ubaid bin Rifaa ko Ismail bin Ubedullah bin Rifaa bhi kaha jata hai."
1211,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' teen log aisey hain jinki taraf Allah Taala qiyamat key din na ( rehmat ki nazar sey) nahin dekhega, na unhen ( gunahon sey) pak kerega, aur unkey liye dardnak azab hoga '' , hamney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! ye kon log hain? ye to nuqsan aur ghatey mein rahey, aap ney farmaya : ''ehsan jataney wala, apney tehband (takhney sey neechey) latkaaney wala padhi. aur jhooti qism key zariey apney saman ko riwaaj deney wala ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Zar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , abu-Huraira, abu-Umama bin Solba, Imran bin Husain aur Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1212,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Allah! meri ummat ko uskey din key ibtidaai hissey mein barkat dey ''sakhr kehtey hain ke aap jab kisi sariya ya lashkar ko rawana kartey to usey din key ibtidaai hissey mein rawana kartey aur sakhr eik tajir aadmi they. jab wo tijarat ka saman ley kar (apney aadmiyon ko) rawana kartey to unhen din key ibtidaai hissey mein rawana kartey, to wo maaldaar ho gaey aur unki dolat badh gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sakhr ghaamidi ki hadees Hasan hai. hum is hadees key ilawa sakhr Ghamidi ki koi aur hadees nahin jantey jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Ibne-Masood , Barida, Anas , ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1213,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jism Mubarak par do motey Qatri kapdey they, jab aap bethtey aur paseena aata to wo aap par bojhal ho jatey , Sham sey falan Yahudi key kapdey aaye . to mainey arz kya : kaash! ! aap uskey paas kisi ko bhejtey aur us sey do kapdey us wadey par kharid letey ke jab gunjaaish hogi to qeemat dey dengey, aap ney uskey paas eik aadmi bheja, to usney kaha : jo wo chahtey hain mujhey malum hai, unka irada hai ke mera maal ya merey daraahim hadap kar lein, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wo jhoota hai, usey khub malum hai ke main logon mein Allah sey sab sey ziyada darney wala aur amanat ko sab sey ziyada ada karney wala hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- isey Shoba ney bhi Imaara bin abi Hafsa sey riwayat kya hai, 3- abu-Daawood Tiyaalisi kehtey hain : eik din Shoba sey is hadees key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : main tum sey is waqt usey nahin bayan kar sakta jab tak ke tum khadey ho kar Hurmi bin Imaara bin abi Hafsa ( jo is hadees key eik Raavi hain (ka sar nahin choomtey aur hurmi ( wahan ( logon mein mojud they, unhoney is hadees sey had darja khush hotey huye ye baat kahi , 4- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Anas aur Asma bint Yazeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1214,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap ki zireh bees saa ghalley key iwaz girwi rakhi hui thi . aap ney isey apney ghar walon key liye liya tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1215,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jo ki roti aur pighli hui charbi jis mein kuch tabdili aa chuki thi ley kar chala, aap ki zireh eik Yahudi key paas bees saa ghalley key iwaz jisey aap ney apney ghar walon key liye ley rakha tha girwi rakhi hui thi padhi. Qatada kehtey hain mainey eik din Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna ke Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar walon key paas eik saa khajoor ya eik saa ghalla Sham ko nahin hota tha jabke us waqt aap key paas no biwiyan thin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1216,"mujh sey Ada bin Khalid bin Hoza ney kaha : kya main tumhen eik tehreer na padhaaun jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey liye likhi thi ? mainey kaha : kyon nahin, zarur padhaiye, phir unhoney eik tehreer nikali , ( jis mein likha tha ( '' ye bai nama hai eik aisi chiz ka jo Ada bin Khalid bin Hoza ney Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey khareedi hai'' , unhoney aap sey ghulam ya laundi ki kharidari us shart key sath ki ke is mein na koi bimari ho, na wo bhagedu ho aur na haram maal ka ho, ye musalman ki musalman sey bai hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye Hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ibaad bin Les ki riwayat sey jantey hain. un sey ye hadees muhaddesin mein sey kaee logon ney riwayat ki hai."
1217,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney naap tol walon sey farmaya : '' tumharey do aisey kaam padhi. kiye gaey hain jis main tum sey pehley ki ummaten halak ho gaeen '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum is hadees ko sirf ba-riwayat Husain bin Qais marfoo jantey hain, aur Husain bin Qais hadees mein zaeef gardaney jatey hain. neez ye sahih sanad sey ibne-Abbas sey moqufan marvi hai."
1218,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik taat jo kajaawe key nichey bichhaya jata hai aur eik piyala bechaa, aap ney farmaya : ''ye taat aur piyala kon khareedeyga? eik aadmi ney arz kiya : main inhen eik dirham mein ley sakta hun.'' , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik dirham sey ziyada kon dega?'' to eik aadmi ney aap ko do dirham diye, to aap ney usi key haath sey ye dono cheezen bech den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. hum isey sirf Akhzar bin Ajlan ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- aur Abdullah Hanfi hi jinhoney Anas sey riwayat ki hai abu-Bakar Hanfi hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log ghanimat aur meeras key saman ko ziyada qeemat deney waley sey bechney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey hain. 4- ye hadees Moa'tamir bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) aur doosrey kaee badey logon ney bhi Akhzar bin Ajlan sey riwayat ki hai."
1219,"Ansaar key eik shakhs ney padhi. apney ghulam ko mudabbir padhi. bana diya (yani us sey ye keh diya ke tum merey marney key baad azad ho), phir wo mar gaya, aur us ghulam key ilawa usney koi aur maal nahin chhoda. to Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey bech diya padhi. aur Naeem bin Abdullah bin Nahaam ney isey kharida. Jabir kehtey hain : wo eik qibti ghulam tha. Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma ki amaarat key pehley saal wo faut huwa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye Jabir bin Abdullah sey aur bhi sanadon sey marvi hai. padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log mudabbir ghulam ko bechney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey hain. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney mudabbir ki bai (saude) ko makrooh jana hai. ye Sufiyan Sory , Malik aur Auzaai ka qol hai."
1220,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maal bechney walon sey bazar mein pahunchney sey pehley ja kar milney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Ali , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , abu Saeed Khudri , ibne-Umar , aur eik aur Sahabi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1221,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bahar sey aaney waley samanon ko bazar mein pahunchney sey pehley aagey ja kar kharid leney sey mana farmaya : agar kisi aadmi ney mil kar kharid liya to sahibe maal ko jab wo bazar mein pahunchey to ikhtiyar hai (chahey to wo bechey chahey to na bechey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Ayub ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney maal bechney walon sey bazar mein pahunchney sey pehley mil kar maal kharidney ko najaaiz kaha hai ye dhokey ki eik qism hai hamarey as-haab (saathiyon) mein sey Shafai waghera ka yehi qol hai.
1222,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shehri bahar sey aaney waley dehati ka maal na bechey padhi. (balke dehati ko khud bechney dey).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Talha , Jabir , Anas , ibne-Abbas ,Abu Yazeed Kasir bin Abdullah key dada Amr bin Auf Muzni aur eik aur Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1223,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi shehri kisi gaaon waley ka saman na farokht karey, tum logon ko (unka saman khud bechney key liye) chhod do. Allah Taala baaz ko baaz key zariey rizq deta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir ki hadees bhi Hasan sahih hai. padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. un logon ney makrooh samjha hai ke shahri bahar sey aaney waley dehati ka saman bechey. 4- aur baaz logon ney rukhsat di hai ke shahri dehati key liye saman kharid sakta hai. 5- Shafai kehtey hain ke shahri ka dehati key saman ko bechna makrooh hai aur agar wo bech dey to bai (sauda) jayez hoga."
1224,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , Zaid bin Sabit , Saad , Jabir , Raafey bin khadij aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaliyon mein khadi kheti ko gehun sey bechney ko muhaaqla kehtey hain, aur darkht par lagi hui khajoor todi gaee khajoor sey bechney ko mazaabna kehtey hain. 4- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log muhaaqla aur mazaabna ko makrooh samajhtey hain."
1225,"Abu Ayaaz Zaid ney Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey gehun ko chhilka utarey huye jau sey bechney key barey mein puchha to unhoney puchha : in dono mein kon afzal hai? unhoney kaha : gehun, to unhoney is sey mana farmaya. aur Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna aap sey tar khajoor sey khushk khajoor kharidney ka masla puchha ja raha tha. to aap ney qarib bethey logon sey puchha : ''kya tar khajoor khushk honey par kam ho jaeyga?'' logon ney kaha haan (kam ho jaeyga), to aap ney is sey mana farmaya. Muallif ney basanad (Wakee an Maalik) isi tarah ki hadees bayan ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Shafai aur hamarey (saathiyon) ka bhi qol hai."
1226,Rasoolullah ney khajoor key darkht ki bai (saude) sey mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke wo khush rang ho jaey (pukhtagi ko pahunch jaey).
1227,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (gehun aur jau waghera key) khoshey bechney sey mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo pukhta ho jaeyn aur aafat sey maamoon ho jaeyn, aap ney kharidar aur bechnewale dono ko mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas , Aaisha , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , Jabir , abu Saeed Khudri aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log phal ki pukhtagi zahir honey sey pehley uskey bechney ko makrooh samajhtey hain, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1228,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney angoor ko bechney sey mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke wo siyah (pukhta) ho jaey. aur daney (ghalley) ko bechney sey mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke wo sakht ho jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey sirf ba-riwayat Hammad bin Salma hi marfoo jantey hain.
1229,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamal key hamal ko bechney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (an Ayoob an Saeed bin Juber an ibne-Abbas) riwayat kiya hai. aur Abdul Wahab Saqafi waghera ney ba-tareeq : (an Ayoob an Saeed bin Jubair w Naafe an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai. aur ye ziyada sahih hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ( حبل الحبلة) (hamal key hamal) sey murad oontni key bachchey ka bachcha hai. ehle-ilm key nazdik ye bai mansookh hai aur ye dhoke ki bai (saude) mein sey eik bai (sauda) hai. 4- is bab mein Abdullah bin Abbas aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain.
1230,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney gharar ke saude aur hasat ke saude sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai, wo gharar ke saude ko makrooh samajhtey hain. 4- Shafai kehtey hain : machhli ki bai jo pani mein ho, bhagey huye ghulam ki bai , aasman mein udtey parindon ki bai aur isi tarah ki dusri bai (saude), gharar ke saude ki qism mein sey hain. 5- aur hasat ke saude sey murad ye hai ke bechney wala kharidney waley sey ye kahey ke jab main teri taraf kankari phenk dun to merey aur terey darmiyan mein bai (sauda) wajib ho gaee. ye sauda munaabiza key jaisa hai. aur ye jahiliyat ki bai (saude) ki qismon mein sey eik qisam thi."
1231,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik bai (saude) mein do bai (saude) karney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Umar aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney eik bai (saude) mein do bai (saude) ki tafseer yun ki hai ke eik bai (saude) mein do bai (saude) ye hai ke maslan kahey : main tumhen ye kapda naqad das rupey mein aur udhaar bees rupey mein bechtaa hun aur bechnewala dono baia'oon (saudon) mein sey kisi eik par juda na ho, (balke baghair kisi eik ki saude key tai kiye hue hi wahan sey chala jaaey) jab wo un dono mein sey kisi eik par juda ho to koi harj nahin ba-sharte-ke un dono mein sey kisi eik par bai (sauda) tey ho gaya ho. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : eik bai (saude) mein do bai (saude) ka mafhoom ye hai ke koi kahey : main apna ye ghar itney rupey mein is shart par bech raha hun ke tum apna ghulam mujh sey itney rupey mein bech do. jab tera ghulam merey liye wajib aur sabit ho jaeyga to mera ghar terey liye wajib aur Sabit ho jaeyga. ye bai (sauda) baghair qeemat tey hona hua. aur kharidar aur bechnewale mein sey koi nahin janta ke uska soda kis chiz par tei huwa hai."
1232,"Maine Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : merey paas kuch log aatey hain aur us chiz ko bechney key liye kehtey hain jo merey paas nahin hoti, to kya main us chiz ko unkey liye bazar sey kharid kar laaun phir farokht karun? aap ney farmaya : '' jo chiz tumharey paas nahin hai uski bai (sauda) na karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, hukm 1234 mein aa raha hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1233,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey us chiz key bechney sey mana farmaya jo merey paas na ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Is-haq bin Mansoor kehtey hain : mainey Ahmed bin Hanbal sey puchha : bai (saude) key sath qarz sey mana farmaney ka kya mafhoom hai? unhoney kaha : uski surat ye hai ke aadmi ko qarz dey phir us sey bai (sauda) karey aur saman ki qeemat ziyada ley aur ye bhi ehtimaal (gumaan) hai ke koi kisi sey kisi chiz ke liye peshgi ki raqam de aur kahey : agar terey paas rupya faraham nahin ho saka to tujhey ye saman merey haath bech dena hoga. Is-haq (ibne Raahwiya) ney bhi wohi baat kahi hai jo Ahmed ney kahi hai. 3- Is-haq bin Mansoor ney kaha : mainey Ahmed sey aisi chiz ki bai (saude) key barey mein puchha jis par kharidar zaamin nahin to unhoney jawab diya, (ye mumaaniat) merey nazdik sirf tuaam (khaane) ki bai (saude) key sath hai jab tak ki kharidar ka us cheez par ikhtiyaar na ho, Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi wohi baat kahi hai jo Ahmed ney kahi hai lekin ye mumaaniat har us chiz mein hai jo naapi ya tauli jati ho. Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : jab  vikreta ye kahey : main aap sey ye kapda is shart key sath bech raha hun ke iski silaaii aur dhulaae merey zimme hai. to bai (saude) ki ye shakal eik bai (saude) mein do shart key qism sey hai. aur jab vikreta ye kahey : main ye kapda aap ko is shart key sath bech raha hun ke iski silaai merey zimme hai. ya vikreta ye kahey : main ye kapda aap ko is shart key sath bech raha hun ke iski dhulaae merey zimme hai, to is bai (saude) mein koi muzaaeqa (harj) nahin hai, ye eik hi shart hai. Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi wohi baat kahi hai jo Ahmed ney kahi hai."
1234,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : bai (saude) key sath qarz jayez nahin hai, aur na eik bai (saude) mein do shartein jayez hain padhi. aur na aisi chiz sey faeyda uthana jayez hai jis ka wo zaamin na ho padhi. aur na aisi chiz ki bai jayez hai jo tumharey paas na ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Hakim bin Hizaam ki hadees Hasan hai (1232, 1233), ye un sey aur bhi sanadon sey marvi hai. aur Ayub Sakhtiyaan aur Abu-Bashar ney isey Yusuf bin Maahik sey aur Yusuf ney Hakim bin Hizaam sey riwayat kiya hai. aur Auf aur Hisham bin Hassan ney is hadees ko ibne Sirin sey aur ibne Sirin ney Hakim bin Hizaam sey aur Hakim bin Hizaam ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai aur ye hadees (riwayat) mursal (munqata') hai. isey (asal mein) ibne Sirin ney Ayub Sakhtiyaan sey aur Ayub ney Yusuf bin Maahik sey aur Yusuf bin Maahik ney Hakim bin Hizaam sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1235,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey us chiz key bechney sey mana farmaya hai jo merey paas nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wakee ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (an Yazeed bin Ibraheem an ibne-Sirin an Ayoob an Hakeem bin Hizaam) riwayat kiya hai aur is mein Yusuf bin Maahik key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. Abdus-Samad ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai (jis mein ibne Sirin ka zikr hai). aur Yahya bin abi Kasir ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (an Yaa'li bin Hakeem an Yousuf bin Maahik an Abdullah bin Asma an Hakeem bin Hizaam an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka usi hadees par amal hai, ye log us chiz ki bai (saude) ko makrooh samajhtey hain jo aadmi key paas na ho."
1236,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wala (meeras) ko bechney aur hiba (hadiya) karney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum isey sirf ba-riwayat Abdullah bin Dinar jantey hain jisey unhoney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai. 3- Yahya bin saleem ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (Abdullah bin umr an Nafey an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai ke aap ney wala (meeras) ko bechney aur hiba karney sey mana farmaya. is sanad mein weham hai. iskey andar Yahya bin Saleem sey weham huwa hai. 4- Abdul Wahab saqafi, aur Abdullah bin Numer aur deegar kaee logon ney ba-tareeq : (an Abdullah bin umr an Abdullah bin Dinar an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai aur ye Yahya bin Saleem ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 5- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai."
1237,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney janwer ko janwer sey udhaar bechney sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Hasan ka samaa (sun'na), Samra sey sahih hai. Ali bin Madini waghera ney aisa hi kaha hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas, Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka janwer ko janwer sey udhaar bechney key masle mein isi hadees par amal hai. Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai. Ahmed bhi isi key qaail hain. 5- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney janwer key janwer sey udhaar bechney ki ijazat di hai. aur yehi Shafai , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1238,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''do janwaron ko eik janwar sey udhaar bechnaa durust nahin hai, haathon haath (naqad) bechney mein koi harj nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1239,"eik ghulam aaya aur usney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hijrat par baiat ki, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nahin jaan sakey ke ye ghulam hai. itney mein uska Malik aa gaya wo us ko maang raha tha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us sey kaha : tum isey mujh sey bech do, chunanche aap ney isey do kaley ghulamon key iwaz kharid liya, phir iskey baad aap kisi sey us waqt tak baiat nahin letey they jab tak ke us sey daryaft na kar letey ke kya wo ghulam hai? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai ke eik ghulam ko do ghulam sey naqada-naqad kharidney mein koi harj nahin hai aur jab udhaar ho to is mein ikhtilaf hai."
1240,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''soney ko soney sey , chaandi ko chaandi sey , khajoor ko khajoor sey , gehun ko gehun sey , namak ko namak sey aur jau ko jau sey barabar barabar becho , jisney ziyada diya ya ziyada liya usney sood ka maamla kiya. soney ko chaandi sey naqda-naqad, jaisey chaho becho , gehun ko khajoor sey naqadan jaisey chaho becho , aur jau ko khajoor sey naqadan jaisey chaho becho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz logon ney is hadees ko Khalid sey isi sanad sey riwayat kiya hai is mein ye hai ke gehun ko jau sey naqda-naqad jaisey chaho becho. 3- baaz logon ney is hadees ko Khalid sey aur Khalid ney Abu-Qulaba sey aur Abu-Qulaba ney Abul Ash'as sey aur Abul Ash'as ney Ubada sey aur Ubada ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai aur is mein ye izafa kiya hai : Khalid kehtey hain : Abu-Qulaba ney kaha : gehun ko jau sey jaisey chaho becho. phir unhoney puri hadees zikr ki. 4- is bab mein abu-Saeed, Abu-Hurera , Bilal aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 5- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo log gehun ko gehun sey aur jau ko jau sey sirf barabar barabar hi bechney ko jayez samajhtey hain aur jab ajnaas mukhtalif ho jaeyn to kami , beshi key sath bechney mein koi harj nahin ba-sharte-ke bai naqad ho. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. Shafai kehtey hain : iski daleel Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka ye farman hai ke jau ko gehun sey naqda naqad jaisey chaho becho. 6- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney jau sey bhi gehun key bechney ko makrooh samjha hai, siwaye iske ke wazan mein masaawi (barabar) hon, pehla qol hi ziyada sahih hai."
1241,"Main aur ibne-Umar dono abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) key paas aaye to unhoney hum sey bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (isey merey dono kanon ney aap sey suna) : ''soney ko soney sey barabar barabar hi becho aur chaandi ko chaandi sey barabar barabar hi becho. eik ko doosrey sey kam aur ziyada na kiya jaey aur ghair mojud ko mojud sey na bech.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- iskey silsiley mein abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Abu-Hurera , Hisham bin Aamir , Bara , Zaid bin Arqam , Fazala bin Ubaid , abu-Bakra , ibne-Umar , Abu-Darda aur Bilal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- magar wo jo ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke wo soney ko soney sey aur chaandi ko chaandi sey kami beshi key sath bechney mein koi muzaaeqa nahin samajhtey they, jabke bai (sauda) naqad ho, aur wo ye bhi kehtey they ke sood to udhaar bechney mein hai aur aisa hi kuchh in key baaz as-haab (saathiyon) sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 5- aur ibne-Abbas sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke abu Saeed Khudri ney jab un sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees bayan ki to unhoney apney qol sey ruju kar liya, pehla qol ziyada sahih hai. ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, aur ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : sarf (soney chaandi ko soney chaandi ke badle bechne)  mein ikhtilaf nahin hai."
1242,"Main Baqee key bazar mein oont bechaa karta tha, main dinaaron sey bechtaa tha, uskey badley chaandi leta tha, aur chaandi sey bechtaa tha aur uskey badley Dinar leta tha, main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur mainey aap ko dekha ke aap Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar sey nikal rahey hain to mainey aap sey iskey barey mein puchha aap ney farmaya : ''qeemat key sath aisa karney mein koi muzaaeqa (harj) nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum is hadees ko sirf Simaak bin Harab hi ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain. 2- Simaak ney isey Saeed bin Juber sey aur Saeed ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai aur Dawud bin Abi Hindiya ney ye hadees Saeed bin Juber sey aur Saeed ney ibne-Umar sey moqufan riwayat ki hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka amal isi hadees par hai ke agar koi soney key badley chaandi ley ya chaandi key badley sona ley , to koi harj nahin hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney isey makrooh jana hai."
1243,"Main (baazaar mein) ye kehtey huye aaya : dirahmon ko (deenar waghera sey) kon badleyga? to Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha aur wo umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas they : hamein apna sona dikhaao, aur jab hamara khaadim aa jaey to hamarey paas aa jaao hum (iskey badley) tumhen chaandi dey den gey. (ye sun kar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! aisa hergiz nahin ho sakta tum isey chaandi hi do warna is ka sona hi lota do, isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''soney key badley chaandi lena sood hai, siwaaye iske ke eik haath sey do, doosrey haath sey lo, gehun key badley gehun lena sood hai, siwaaye iske ke eik haath sey do , doosrey haath sey lo , jau key badley jau lena sood hai siwaaye iske ke eik haath sey do , doosrey haath sey lo , aur khajoor key badley khajoor lena sood hai siwaaye iske ke eik haath sey do , doosrey haath sey l.o'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. « إلاھاء وھاء » ka mafhoom hai naqda-naqad."
1244,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' jisney «تأبیر» padhi. (pewand kaari) key baad khajoor ka darkht kharid to uska phal bechney waley hi ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala (khareedtey waqt phal ki) shart laga ley. aur jisney koi aisa ghulam kharid jis key paas maal ho to uska maal bechney waley hi ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala ( khareedtey waqt maal ki) shart laga ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah aur bhi turq sey basanad (an Zohri an Salim an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) sey riwayat hai aap ney farmaya : ''jisney pewand-kaari key baad khajoor ka darkht kharid to uska phal bechney waley hi ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala ( darkht key sath phal ki bhi) shart laga ley aur jisney koi aisa ghulam kharid jis key paas maal ho to uska maal bechney waley ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala ( ghulam key sath maal ki bhi) shart laga ley.''  3- ye Nafey sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney ibne-Umar sey aur ibne-Umar ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''jisney khajoor ka koi darkht kharid jiski pewand-kaari ki ja chuki ho to uska phal bechney waley hi ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala ( darkht key sath phal ki bhi) shart laga ley.''  4- Nafey sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo ibne-Umar sey riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke jisney koi ghulam bechaa jis key paas maal ho to uska maal bechney waley hi ka hoga siwaaye iske ke kharidney wala (ghulam key sath maal ki bhi) shart laga ley. 5- isi tarah Ubedullah bin umr waghera ney Nafey sey dono hadisein riwayat ki hain. 6- neez (isi ke saath) baaz logon ney ye hadees Nafey sey , Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 7- Ikrima bin Khalid ney ibne-Umar sey ibne-Umar ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Salim ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 8- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Zohri ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq : (an Salim an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai is baab mein sab sey ziyada sahih hai. 9- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 10- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
1245,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''bechney wala aur kharidney wala dono ko jab tak wo juda na hon bai (saude) ko baqi rakhney aur fasakh (radd) karney ka ikhtiyar hai padhi. ya wo dono ikhtiyar ki shart kar lein.''  Nafey kehtey hain : jab ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma koi chiz khareedtey aur bethey hotey to khadey ho jatey taake bai (sauda) wajib (pakka) ho jaey (aur ikhtiyar baqi na rahey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza , Hakim bin Hizaam, Abdullah bin Abbas , Abdullah bin Amr , Samura aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. ye log kehtey hain ke تفرق sey murad jismani judai hai na ke qauli judai, yani majlis sey judai murad hai guftgu ka mauzoo badalna murad nahin. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol «مالم يتفرقا» sey murad qauli judai hai, pehla qol ziyada sahih hai, isliye ke ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney hi is ko Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai. aur wo apni riwayat karda hadees ka maana ziyada jantey hain aur un sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke jab wo bai wajib ( pakki ( karney ka irada kartey to (majlis sey uth kar) chal detey taake bai wajib ho jaey. 5- abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1246,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''بائع ( bechney wala (aur mushtari (kharidney wala) ( kharidar ( jab tak juda na hon padhi. dono ko bai (saude) key baqi rakhney aur fasakh (radd) kar deney ka ikhtiyar hai, agar wo dono sach kahin aur saaman ki khoobi aur kharabi wazeh kar den to un ki bai (saude) mein barkat di jaeygi aur agar un dono ney aeb ko chupaya aur jhooti baaten kahin to un ki bai (saude) ki barkat khatam kar di jaeygi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- isi tarah abu-Barza Aslami sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke do aadmi eik ghodey ki bai (sauda) kerney key baad uska muqadma ley kar unkey paas aaye, wo log eik kashti mein they. abu-Barza ney kaha : main nahin samajhta ke tum dono juda huye ho aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : '' bechne wala aur kharidar jab tak (majlis sey) juda na hon ikhtiyar hai.''  3- ehle-koofa waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm is taraf gaey hain ke judai qol sey hogi , yehi Sufiyan Sory ka qol hai, aur isi tarah Malik bin Anas sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 4- aur ibne-Mubarak ka kehna hai ke main is maslak ko kaisey radd kar dun? jabke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey waarid hadees sahih hai. 5- aur unhoney is ko qawi kaha hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol « إلا بيع الخيار » ka matlab ye hai ke kharidar bechne wale ko bai (saude/sauda) key wajib karney key baad ikhtiyar dedey , phir jab bechne wala bai (saude/sauda) ko ikhtiyar kar ley to uskey baad us ko bai (saude/sauda) fasakh (radd) karney ka ikhtiyar nahin hoga, agar-che wo dono juda na huye hun. isi tarah Shafai waghera ney iski tafseer ki hai. 6- aur jo log jismani judai (تفرق بالابدان ( key qaail hain unkey qol ko Abdullah bin Amr ki hadees taqwiyat (mazbuti) dey rahi hai jisey wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain (aagey hi aa rahi hai)."
1247,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''بائع ( bechney wala (aur مشتری ( kharidar )  jab tak juda na hon in ko ikhtiyar hai siwaye iske ke bai (sauda)  khiyaar ho (tab juda honey key baad bhi wapsi ka ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai), aur بائع (bechney wale)  key liye jayez nahin hai ke apney sathi (kharidar) sey us dar sey juda ho jaey ke wo bai (saude) ko fasakh (radd) kar dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur is ka maana yehi hai ke bai (saude) key baad wo kharidar sey juda ho jaey is dar sey ke wo isey fasakh (radd) kar dega aur agar judai sirf kalam sey ho jati, aur bai (saude) key baad kharidar ko ikhtiyar na hota to is hadees ka koi maana na hoga jo ke aap ney farmaya hai : ''بائع (bechney wala) key liye jayez nahin hai ke wo kharidar sey is dar sey juda ho jaey ke wo uski bai (saude) ko fasakh (radd) kar dega.''"
1248,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baaey (bechney wala) aur mushtari (kharidney wala) bai (saude) (ki majlis) sey raza-mandi key sath hi juda hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
1249,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bai (saude) key baad eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ko ikhtiyar diya. ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1250,"Eik aadmi kharid aur farokht karney mein boda padhi. tha aur wo (aksar) kharid aur farokht karta tha, uskey ghar waley Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur un logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap is ko (kharid aur farokht sey) rok dijiye, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us ko bulwaya aur usey us sey mana farma diya. usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main bai (saude) sey baaz rehney par sabr nahin kar sakoonga, aap ney farmaya : ''(achchha) jab tum bai (sauda) karo to ye keh liya karo ke eik haath sey do aur doosrey haath sey lo aur koi dhoka-dhadi nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke azad shakhs ko kharid aur farokht sey us waqt roka ja sakta hai jab wo kamzor aql ka ho, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur baaz log azad baligh ko bai (saude) sey rokney ko durust nahin samajhtey hain."
1251,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney koi aisa janwer kharid jis ka doodh than mein (kaee dino sey) rok diya gaya ho, to jab wo uska doodh dohai to usey ikhtiyar hai agar wo chahey to eik saa khajoor key sath us ko wapis kar dey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Anas aur eik aur Sahaba sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1252,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney koi aisa janwer kharid jiska doodh than mein rok diya gaya ho to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai. agar wo usey wapis karey to uskey sath eik saa koi ghalla bhi wapis karey jo gehun na ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hamarey as-haab (saathiyon) ka isi par amal hai. in hi mein Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya hain. aap key qol (لاسمراء) ka matlab (لابُرّ) hai yani gehun na ho (khaney ki koi aur chiz ho, pichli hadees mein khajoor ka tazkira hai)."
1253,Unhoney (raastey mein) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik oont bechaa aur apney ghar walon tak sawar ho kar janey ki shart rakhi lagai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye aur bhi sanadon sey Jabir sey marvi hai. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log bai (saude) mein shart ko jayez samajhtey hain jab shart eik ho. yehi qol Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka hai. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke bai (saude) mein shart jayez nahin hai aur jab is mein shart ho to bai (sauda) puri nahin hogi.
1254,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sawari ka janwer jab rehan rakha ho to is par sawari ki jaey aur doodh wala janwer jab girwi rakha ho to uska doodh piya jaey, aur jo sawari karey aur doodh piye janwer ka kharch usi key zimme hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum isey ba-riwayat Aamir Shaa'bi hi marfoo jantey hain, unhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai aur kaee logon ney is hadees ko Aamash sey riwayat kiya hai aur Aamash ney abu-Saaleh sey aur abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey mauqufan riwayat ki hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. aur yehi qol Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke rehan sey kisi tarah ka faeyda uthana durust nahin hai."
1255,"Mainey khaibar key din baara Dinar main eik haar kharid , jis mein soney aur jawaharat jadey huye they, mainey unhen (tod-kar) juda-juda kiya to mujhey is mein baara Dinar sey ziyada miley. mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uska zikr kya to aap ney farmaya : ''(soney aur jawaharat jadey huye haar) na bechey jaeyn jab tak unhen juda juda na kar liya jaey.'' isi tarah Muallif ney Quteba sey isi sanad sey hadees riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log chaandi jadi hui talwaar ya kamar band ya isi jaisi doosriy chizon ko dirham sey farokht karna durust nahin samajhtey hain, jab tak ke un sey chaandi alag na kar li jaey. ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. 3- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney iski ijazat di hai."
1256,"Unhoney Barira (laundi) ko khareednaa chaha, to Bareera key malikon ney walaa ki shart lagai to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Aaisha sey farmaya : '' tum usey kharid lo, (aur azad kar do) isliye ke walaa to usi ka hoga jo qeemat ada karey, ya jo nemat (azad karney) ka Malik ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1257,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen eik Dinar mein qurbani ka janwer kharidney key liye bheja , to unhoney qurbani ka eik janwer kharid (phir usey do Dinar mein bech diya), is mein unhen eik Dinar ka faeyda huwa , phir unhoney uski jagah eik Dinar mein doosra janwer kharida, qurbani ka janwer aur eik Dinar ley kar wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye, to aap ney farmaya : ''bakri ki qurbani kar do aur Dinar ko sadqa kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Hakim bin Hizaam ki hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, aur merey nazdik Habib bin abi Sabit ka samaa (sun'na), Hakeem bin Hizaam sey Sabit nahin hai."
1258,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bakri kharidney key liye mujhey eik Dinar diya, to mainey us sey do bakriyan khareedin, phir un mein sey eik ko eik Dinar mein bech diya aur eik bakri aur eik Dinar ley kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya, aur aap sey tamam maamla bayan kiya aur aap ney farmaya : ''Allah tumhen tumharey haath key sodey mein barkat dey.''  phir uskey baad wo Koofa key kunasa ki taraf jatey aur bahut ziyada munaafa kamatey they. chunanche wo Koofa key sab sey ziyada maaldaar aadmi bin gaey. Muallif ney Ahmed bin Saeed Darmi key turq sey Zuber bin Khirrit sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain aur wo isi key qaail hain aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ko nahin liya hai, inhin logon mein Shafai aur Hammad bin Zaid Saeed bin Zaid key bhai hain."
1259,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab makatib ghulam (wo ghulam jo apni qeemat khud ada karke apne aap ko azaad kara le) kisi diyat ya meeras ka mustahiq ho to usi key mutabiq wo hissey paeyga jitna wo azad kya ja chuka hai.'' neez (isi ke saath) aap ney farmaya : ''makatib jitna zare-kitaabat ada kar chuka hai itni azadi key mutabiq diyat diya jaeyga aur jo baqi hai uskey mutabiq ghulam ki diyat di jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- isi tarah Yahya bin abi Kasir ney Ikrima sey aur ikrima ney ibne-Abbas sey aur ibne-Abbas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- lekin Khalid Haza ney bhi Ikrima sey (riwayat ki hai magar unkey mutabiq) Ikrima ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key qol sey riwayat ki hai. 5- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai. aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke jab tak makatib par eik dirham bhi baqi hai wo ghulam hai, Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1260,Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko khutbe key doran kehtey suna : ''jo apney ghulam sey sau auqiya (baara sau dirham) par makatibat (likhaee) karey aur wo das auqiya key ilawa tamam ada kar dey phir baqi ki adaegi sey wo aajiz rahey to wo ghulam hi rahega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Hujjaaj bin Irtaat ney bhi Amr bin Shuaib sey Isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke jab tak makatib par kuch bhi zare (maal) kitaabat baqi hai wo ghulam hi rahega۔
1261,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey kisi key makatib ghulam key paas itni raqam ho ke wo zare (maal) kitaabat ada kar sakey to usey us sey parda karna chahiye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka is hadees par amal zaiye darna aur taqwa aur ehtiyat hai. ye log kehtey hain ke makatib ghulam jab tak zare kitaabat na ada kar dey azad nahin hoga agar-che uskey paas zare kitaabat ada karney key liye raqam mojud ho.
1262,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo (qarz daar) aadmi muflis ho jaey aur (qarz deney wala) aadmi apna saman uskey paas bilkul waise hi paey to wo us saman ka doosrey sey ziyada mustahiq hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Samura aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : wo bhi doosrey qarz khuwahon (chaahne walon) ki tarah hoga, yehi ehle-Koofa ka bhi qol hai."
1263,"hamarey paas eik yatim ki sharab thi, jab Sura al-Maeyda nazil hui (jis mein sharab ki hurmat mazkur (zikr) hai) to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha aur arz kiya ke wo eik yatim ki hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''usey baha do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur bhi sanadon sey ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- is bab mein Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm isi key qaail hain, ye log sharab ka sirka bananey ko makrooh samajhtey hain, is wajeh sey isey makrooh qarar diya gaya hai ke musalman key ghar mein sharab rahey yahan tak ke wo sirka bin jaey ( Allah ki qism اعلم ). ‏‏‏‏ 5- baaz logon ney sharab key sirke ki ijazat di hai jab wo khud sirka bin jaey."
1264,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo tumharey paas amanat rakhey usey amanat lotaao padhi. aur jo tumharey sath khayanat karey uskey sath (bhi) khayanat na karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke jab aadmi ka kisi doosrey ke zimme koi chiz ho aur wo usey ley kar chala jaey phir us janey waley ki koi chiz uskey haath mein aaye to uskey liye jayez nahin hai ke is mein sey itna rok ley jitna wo uska ley kar gaya hai. 3- Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney iski ijazat di hai, aur yehi Sory ka bhi qol hai, wo kehtey hain : agar uskey zimme dirham ho aur) bator amanat ( uskey paas uskey Dinar aagey to uskey liye jayez nahin ke wo apney daraahim key badley usey rok ley, albatta uskey paas uskey daraahim aa jaeyn to us waqt uskey liye durust hoga ke uskey daraahim mein sey itna rok ley jitna uskey zimme uska hai."
1265,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Hajjatul-wadaa key saal khutbe mein farmatey suna : ''Udhaar li hui chiz lautaai jaeygi, zaamin ko tawaan (jurmaana) dena hoga aur qarz adaa karna wajib hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye abu-Umama key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aur bhi tareeq sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Samura , Safwan bin Umayya aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1266,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo kuchh haath ney liya hai jab tak wo usey ada na kar dey uskey zimme hai.''  Qatada kehtey hain : phir Hasan Basri is hadees ko bhool gaey aur kehney lagey ''jisney udhaar li hai'' wo tera ameen hai, is par tawaan (jurmaana) nahin hai, yani udhaar li hui chiz talaf (khatam) honey par tawaan nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain ye log kehtey hain : udhaar leney wala zaamin hota hai. aur yehi Shafai aur Ahmed ka bhi qol hai. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke Aariyatan (udhaar) leney waley par tawaan (jurmaana) nahin hai, siwaye iske ke wo saaman waley ki mukhalifat karey. Sory aur ehle-koofa ka yehi qol hai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain."
1267,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' gunehgar hi  zakhira andozi (jama karna) karta hai.''  Muhammad bin Ibrahim kehtey hain : mainey Saeed bin Al Musaiyab sey kaha : abu Muhammad ! aap to zakhira andozi kartey hain? unhoney kaha : Maamar bhi Zakhira andozi kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Maamar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Saeed bin Musaiyab sey marvi hai, wo tel, gehun aur isi tarah ki chizon ki zakhira andozi (jama karna) kartey they. 3- is bab mein umr , Ali , abu-Umama , aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. un logon ney khaney ki zakhira andozi najaaiz kaha hai. 5- baaz ehle-ilm ney khaney key ilawa deegar ashiya ki zakhira andozi ki ijazat di hai. 6- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : rui , dabaaghat di hui bakri ki khaal , aur isi tarah ki chizon ki zakhira andozi mein koi harj nahin hai."
1268,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(baazaar mein aaney waley qafila tijarat ka bazar sey pehley) istaqbal na karo, janwer key than mein doodh na roko (taake kharidar dhoka kha jaey) aur (jhoota kharidar bin kar) eik doosrey ka saman na farokht karaao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log aisey janwer ki bai (saude) ko jis ka doodh than mein rok liya gaya ho jayez nahin samajhtey. 4- muhaffala aisey janwer ko kehtey hain jis ka doodh than mein chhodey rakha gaya ho, uska Malik kuchh din sey usey na dohtaa hota ke uski than mein doodh jama ho jaey aur kharidar us sey dhoka kha jaey. ye faraib aur dhoke hi ki eik shakal hai."
1269,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney jhooti qism khai taake uskey zariey wo kisi musalman ka maal hathiya ley to wo Allah Taala sey is haal mein milega ke Allah Taala us sey naraz hoga.'' Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Allah ki qism ! aap ney merey silsiley mein ye hadees bayan farmaai thi. merey aur eik Yahudi key darmiyan eik zamin mushtarak thi, usney merey hissey ka inkar kiya to main usey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey puchha : ''kya tumharey paas koi gawah hai? ''main ney arz kiya : nahin, to aap ney Yahudi sey farmaya : ''tum qism khaao'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! wo to qism kha lega aur mera maal hazam kar ley ga. is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaee :«إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا» ''aur jo log Allah key qarar aur apni qasmon key iwaz thoda sa mol hasil kartey hain. . . .'' (Aale Imran : 77). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Wayl bin Hajar , abu-Musa , abu-Umama bin Solba Ansari aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1270,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab baaey (bechney wala) aur mushtari (kharidney wala) mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to baat baaey (bechney wala) ki maana jaeygi, aur mushtari (kharidney wala) ko ikhtiyar hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees mursal hai, Aun bin Abdullah ney ibne-Masood ko nahin paya. 2- aur Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman sey bhi ye hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney ibne-Masood sey aur ibne-Masood ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. aur ye riwayat bhi mursal hai. 3- Is-haq bin Mansoor kehtey hain : mainey Ahmed sey puchha : jab baaey (bechney wala) aur mushtari (kharidney wala) mein ikhtilaf ho jaey aur koi gawah na ho to kis ki baat taslim ki jaeygi? unhoney kaha : baat wohi moatabar hogi jo saaman ka Malik kaheyga, ya phir dono apni apni chiz wapis ley lein yani baaey (bechney wala) saaman wapis ley ley aur mushtari (kharidney wala) qeemat. Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi yahi kaha hai jo Ahmed ney kaha hai. 4- aur baat jiski bhi maana jaey uskey zimme qism khana hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai, inhi mein Shureh bhi hain."
1271,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pani bechney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ayas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Buhesa , Buhesa key baap , Abu-Hurera , Aaisha , Anas aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, in logon ney pani bechney ko najaaiz kaha hai, yehi ibne-Mubarak Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney pani bechney ki ijazat di hai, jin mein Hasan Basri bhi shamil hain."
1272,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zarurat sey zayed pani sey na roka jaey ke uskey sabab ghaas sey rok diya jaey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1273,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nar ko mada par chhodney ki ujrat leney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Anas aur abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. baaz ulama ney is kaam par bakhshish qubul karney ki ijazat di hai, jamhur (ziyada aalimon) key nazdik ye haram hai."
1274,"Qabeela Kilaab key eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey nar ko mada par chhodney ki ujrat leney key barey mein puchha to aap ney isey mana kar diya, phir usney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum mada par nar chhodtey hain to hamein bakhshish di jati hai (to is ka hukm kya hai?) aap ney isey bakhshish leney ki ijazat dey di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey sirf Ibrahim bin Humed hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey unhoney Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat ki hai."
1275,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pachhna laganey waley ki kamai khabees (ghatiya) hai padhi. zaaniya ki ujrat napak padhi. hai aur kuttey ki qeemat napak hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , ibne-Masood , abu-Masood , Jabir , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Umar aur Abdullah ibn Jaafar Raziallahu anhum sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. in logon ney kuttey ki qeemat ko najaaiz jaana hai, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm ney shikari kuttey ki qeemat ki ijazat di hai."
1276,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki kamai aur kaahin ki mithaai sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1277,"Unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey pachhna laganey waley ki ujrat ki ijazat talab ki, to aap ney unhen is sey mana farmaya padhi. lekin wo baar-baar aap sey poochhtey aur ijazat talab kartey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : ''isey apney oont key chaare par kharch karo ya apney ghulam ko khila do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mahisa ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Raafey bin Khadees, Juhaifa, Jabir aur Saaib bin Yazeed sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- Ahmed kehtey hain : agar mujh sey koi pachhna laganey wala mazduri talab karey to main nahin dunga aur daleel mein yehi hadees pesh karunga."
1278,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey pachhna laganey waley ki kamai key barey mein puchha gaya to Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pachhna lagwaayaa , aur aap ko pachhna laganey waley abu-Taiba they, to aap ney unhen do saa ghalla deney ka hukm diya aur unkey malikon sey baat ki, to unhoney abu-Taiba key Khiraaj (tex) mein kami kar di aur aap ney farmaya : ''jin chizon sey tum dawaa kartey ho un mein sab sey afzal pachhna hai.'' ya farmaya : ''tumhari behtar dawaaon mein sey pachhna hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney pachhna laganey waley ki ujrat ko jayez qarar diya hai. yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
1279,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuttey aur billi ki qeemat sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad mein iztirab hai. billi ki qeemat key barey mein ye sahih nahin hai, 2- ye hadees Aamash sey marvi hai unhoney apney baaz as-haab sey riwayat ki hai aur usney Jabir sey, ye log Aamash sey is hadees ki riwayat mein iztirab ka shikar hain, 3- aur ibn Fazal ney is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey b-tareeq : « Aamash , an abi Hazim, an abi Hurera , an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat ki hai, 4- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney billi ki qeemat ko najaaiz kaha hai, 5- aur baaz logon ney uski rukhsat di hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
1280,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney billi aur uski qeemat khaney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- aur hum abdur-Razzaaq key ilawa kisi badey muhaddis ko nahin jantey jisney Amr bin Zaid sey riwayat ki ho."
1281,"kuttey ki qeemat sey) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ( mana farmaya hai siwaye shikari kuttey ki qeemat key. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is tareeq sey sahih nahin hai, 2- abu-Mohazzim ka naam Yazeed bin Sufiyan hai, unkey silsiley mein Shoba bin hujjaaj ney kalam kya hai aur un ki tazeef ki hai, 3- aur Jabir sey marvi hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, aur iski sanad bhi sahih nahin hai (dekhein Sahiha : 2971)"
1282,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' gaaney wali laundiyon ko na becho aur na unhen kharido , aur na unhen ( gaanaa ( sikhaao , un ki tijarat mein khair o barkat nahin hai aur un ki qeemat haram hai. aur usi jaisi chizon key barey mein ye aayat utri hai : (ومن الناس من يشتري لهو الحديث ليضل an سبيل الله)''aur baaz log aisey hain jo laghw baaton ko kharid letey hain taake logon ko Allah ki raah sey behkaaeyn'' (luqman : 6) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Umama ki hadees ko hum is tarah sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain, aur baaz ehle-ilm ney Ali bin Yazeed key barey mein kalam kya hai aur unki tazeef ki hai. aur ye Sham key rehney waley hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1283,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' jo shakhs maa aur uskey bachey key darmiyan judai dalega Allah Taala qiyamat key din uskey aur uskey doston key darmiyan judai dal dega '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1284,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey do ghulam diye jo aapas mein bhai they, mainey un mein sey eik ko bech diya, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey puchha : '' Ali ! tumhara ghulam kya huwa ?'', mainey aap ko bataya (ke mainey eik ko bech diya hai) to aap ney farmaya : ''usey wapis lota lo, usey wapis lota lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm bechtey waqt (rishtey-daar) qaidiyon key darmiyan judai dalney ko najaaiz kaha hai, 3- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney un ladkon key darmiyan judai ko jayez qarar diya hai jo sar zamin Islam mein paida huye hain. pehla qol hi ziyada sahih hai, 4- Ibrahim Nakhai sey marvi hai ke unhoney bechtey waqt maa aur uskey ladkey key darmiyan tafriq, chunanche un par ye aetraz kya gaya to unhoney kaha : mainey uski maa sey uski ijazat maangi to wo is par razi hai."
1285,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney faisla kya ke faaedey ka istehqaaq zaamin honey ki buniyad par hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye aur bhi sanadon sey marvi hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1286,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney faisla kya ke faeyda ka istehqaaq zaamin honey ki buniyad par hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Ismail ney is hadees ko umr bin Ali ki riwayat sey gharib jana hai. mainey puchha : kya aap ki nazar mein is mein tadlees hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, 3- Muslim bin Khalid Zanji ney is hadees ko Hisham bin Urwa sey riwayat kya hai. 4- Jareer ney bhi usey Hisham sey riwayat kya hai, 5- aur kaha jata hai ke Jareer ki hadees mein tadlees hai, is mein Jareer ney tadlees ki hai, unhoney usey Hisham bin Urwa sey nahin suna hai, 6- « الخراج بالضمان » ki tafseer ye hai ke aadmi ghulam khareedey aur us sey mazduri kiraaey phir is mein koi aeb dekhey aur us ko bechney waley key paas lota dey, to ghulam ki jo mazduri aur faeyda hai wo kharidney waley ka hoga. isliye ke agar ghulam halak ho jata to mushtari (kharidney wala) ( kharidar (ka maal halak hota. ye aur is tarah key masaayel mein faeydey ka istehqaaq zaamin honey ki wajeh sey hota hai."
1287,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs kisi baagh mein dakhil ho to ( phal ( khaye , kapdon mein baandh kar na ley jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai. hum isey is tareeq sey sirf Yahya bin Suleim hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr, Ibaad bin Shurehbil, Raafey bin Amr, Umer Maula Aabi-al-laham aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney raah geer key liye phal khaney ki rukhsat di hai. aur baaz ney isey najaaiz kaha hai, illa ye ke qeemat ada kar key ho."
1288,"mein ansaar key khajoor key darakhton par pathar maarta tha, un logon ney mujhey pakad liya aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley gaey aap ney puchha : ''Raafey! tum unkey khajoor key darakhton par pathar kyon maartey ho?'' mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! bhook ki wajeh sey , aap ney farmaya : '' pathar mat maaro , jo khud-b-khud gir jaey usey khaao Allah tumhen aasooda aur sairab karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1289,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey latkey huye phal key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''jo zarurat mand is mein sey) zarurat key mutabiq ( ley ley aur kapdey mein jama karney wala na ho to is par koi muaakhza nahin hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
1290,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muhaaqla , muzabna padhi. mukhabira padhi. aur bey mein kuch chizon ko mustashnaa karney sey mana farmaya padhi. illa ye ke istasna ki hui chiz malum ho . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees us tareeq sey ba-riwayat Yunus bin Ubaid jisey Yunus ney Ata sey aur Ata ney Jabir sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1291,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to usey na bechey jab tak ke is par qabza na kar ley '', ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : main har chiz ko ghalley hi key misl samajhta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir, ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un logon ney ghalla ki bai ko najaaiz kaha hai. jab tak mushtari (kharidney wala) is par qabza na kar ley , 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney qabza sey pehley us shakhs ko bechney ki rukhsat di hai jo koi aisi chiz khareedey jo naapi aur toli na jati ho aur na khai aur pi jati ho, 5- ehle-ilm key nazdik sakhti ghalley key silsiley mein hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1292,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey koi doosrey ki bey par bai na karey padhi. aur na koi kisi key shaadi key pegham par pegham dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Samra Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya aadmi apney bhai key bhaaw par bhaaw na karey 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi is hadees mein bai sey murad bhaaw-taaw aur mol tol hai."
1293,"unhoney arz kya : Allah key Nabi ! mainey un yatimon key liye sharab khareedi thi jo meri parwarish mein hain. ( uska kya hukm hai? (aap ney farmaya : '' sharab baha do aur matkey tod do ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees ko Sory ney b-tareeq : (السدي ، an يحيى بن عباد ، an أنس) riwayat kya hai ke abu-Talha aap key paas they padhi. , aur ye Les ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Aaisha , abu-Saeed , ibne-Masood , ibne-Umar , aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1294,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : kya sharab ka sirka banaya ja sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1295,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sharab ki wajeh sey '' das aadmiyon par lanat bheji : uskey nichodwaney waley par , uskey peeney waley par , uskey ley janey waley par , uskey mangwaney waley par, aur jis key liye ley jaai jaey us par, uskey pilaney waley par, aur uskey bechney waley par, uski qeemat khaney waley par, usko kharidney waley par aur jis key liye khareedi gaee ho us par''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey gharib hai, 2- aur isi hadees ki tarah ibne-Abbas, ibne-Masood aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi marvi hai jisey ye log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
1296,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi kisi rewad key paas ( doodh peeney ( aaye to agar un mein unka Malik mojud ho to us sey ijazat ley, agar wo ijazat dedey to doodh pi ley. agar un mein koi na ho to teen baar aawaz lagaey, agar koi jawab dey to us sey ijazat ley ley, aur agar koi jawab na dey to doodh pi ley lekin sath na ley jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samra ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr aur abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain, 4- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain ke Samra sey Hasan ka samaa, Sabit hai, 5- baaz muhaddesin ney Hasan ki riwayat mein jisey unhoney Samra sey riwayat ki hai kalam kya hai, wo log kehtey hain ke Hasan Samra key saheefa sey hadees riwayat kartey they padhi. ."
1297,"unhoney Fateh Makka key saal Makka key andar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' Allah aur uskey Rasool ney sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki bai ko haram qarar diya hai'' , arz kya gaya, Allah key Rasool ! mujhey murdar ki charbi key barey mein bataiye , usey kashtiyon pe mala jata hai, chamdon pe lagaya jata hai, aur log us sey chiragh jalaatey hain? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin, ye jayez nahin, ye haram hai'' , phir aap ney usi waqt farmaya : '' Yahud par Allah ki maar ho, Allah ney unkey liye charbi haram qarar dey di, to unhoney us ko pighlaaya phir usey becha aur uski qeemat khai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
1298,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' buri misal hamarey liye munasib nahin, hadiya dey kar wapis leney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo qai kar key chaat-ta hai'' padhi. ."
1299,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi key liye jayez nahin ke koi Atiya dey kar usey wapis ley siwaye baap key jo apney betey ko dey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka usi hadees par amal hai. ye log kehtey hain ke jo kisi zii Mohrim ko koi chiz bator hiba dey to phir usey wapis leney ka ikhtiyar nahin, aur jo kisi ghair zii Mohrim ko koi chiz bator hiba dey to uskey liye usey wapis lena jayez hai jab usey uska badla na diya gaya ho, yehi Sory ka qol hai, 3- aur Shafai kehtey hain : kisi key liye jayez nahin ke wo kisi ko koi Atiya dey phir usey wapis ley , siwaye baap key jo apney betey ko dey , Shafai ney Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees sey istidlaal kya hai jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' kisi key liye jayez nahin ke koi Atiya dey kar usey wapis ley siwaye baap key jo apney betey ko dey''."
1300,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muhaaqla aur muzaabna sey mana farmaya , albatta aap ney araayaa walon ko andaza laga kar usey itni hi khajoor mein bechney ki ijazat di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees ko Muhammad bin Is-haq ney isi tarah riwayat kya hai. aur Ayub, Ubedullah bin umr aur Malik bin Anas ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muhaaqla aur muzabna sey mana farmaya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. aur isi sanad sey ibne-Umar ney Zaid bin Sabit sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap ney bai araaya ki ijazat di. aur ye Muhammad bin Is-haq ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
1301,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney paanch wasq sey kam mein araaya key bechney ki ijazat di hai ya aisey hi kuch aap ney farmaya. Raavi ko shak hai ke hadees key yehi alfaz hain ya kuch farq hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1302,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney andaza laga kar araayaa (hadiye ke taur par di jane wali jins ko muzaabna ki shakl mein) ko bechney ki ijazat di hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. jis mein Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi mein shamil hain. ye log kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney minjumla (sabki sab) jin chizon sey mana farmaya hai us sey araayaa (hadiye ke taur par di jane wali jins ko muzaabna ki shakl mein) mustashnaa (alag) hai, isliye ke aap ney muhaaqla aur muzaabna sey mana farmaya hai. in logon ney Zaid bin Sabit aur Abu-Hurera ki hadees sey daleel di  hai inka kehna hai ke iskey liye paanch wasq sey kam khareednaa jayez hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik iska mafhoom ye hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paishe-nazar is silsiley mein dheel chhodna aur gunjaaish dena hai, isliye ke araayaa walon ney aap sey shikayat ki aur arz kiya ke khushk khajoor key siwa hamein koi aur chiz muyassar nahin jis sey hum taza khajoor kharid saken. to aap ney unhen paanch wasq sey kam mein kharidney ki ijazat dey di taake wo taza khajoor kha saken."
1303,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney muzaabna saude yani sookhi khajuron key iwaz darkht par lagi khajoor bechney sey mana farmaya, albatta aap ney araayaa walon ko ijazat di, aur khushk angoor key iwaz tar angoor bechney sey aur andaza laga kar koi bhi phal bechney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is tareeq sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1304,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum najsh na karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un logon ney (najsh) ko najaaiz kaha hai, 4- (najsh) ye hai ke aisa aadmi jo saaman key achchhey burey ki tamiz rakhta ho saaman waley key paas aaye aur asal qeemat sey badha kar saaman ki qeemat lagaey aur ye aisey waqt ho jab kharidar uskey paas mojud ho, maqsad sirf ye ho ke is sey kharidar dhoka kha jaey aur wo (daam badha chadha kar laganey wala) kharidney ka khayal na rakhta ho balke sirf ye chahta ho ke uski qeemat laganey ki wajeh sey kharidar dhoka kha jaey. ye dhoke hi ki eik qisam hai. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : agar koi aadmi (najsh) karta hai to apney is kaam ki wajeh sey wo yani (najsh) karney wala gunehgar hoga aur bai (sauda) jayez hogi , isliye ke bechney wala to (najsh) nahin kar raha hai."
1305,"Main aur Makhrima Abdi dono maqame hijr sey eik kapda ley aaye , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey paas tashrif laye aur aap ney hum sey eik paajaame ka mol-bhaaw kiya. merey paas eik tolney wala tha jo ujrat ley kar tolta tha to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tolney waley sey farmaya : ''jhuka kar tol.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Suwed (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm jhuka kar tolney ko mustahab samajhtey hain. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- aur Shoba ney bhi is hadees ko Simaak sey riwayat kiya hai, lekin unhoney « an Suwed bin Qais » ki jagah « an abi Safwan » kaha hai phir aagey hadees zikr ki hai."
1306,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi tang dast (qarz-daar) ko mohlat dey ya uska kuchh qarz maaf kar dey, to Allah isey qiyamat key din apney arsh key saye key nichey jagah dega jis din uskey saye key ilawa koi aur saya na hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu Yosr (Kaab bin Amr), abu-Qatada , Huzefa , ibne-Masood , Ubada aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1307,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum sey pehli ummaton mein sey eik aadmi ka hisab (uski maut key baad) liya gaya, to uskey paas koi neki nahin mili, siwaye iskey ke wo eik maaldaar aadmi tha, logon sey len-den karta tha aur apney khaadimon ko hukm deta tha ke (taqaazey key waqt) tang dast sey darguzar karen, to Allah Taala ney (farishton sey) farmaya : hum is sey ziyada uskey (darguzar key) haqdaar hain, tum log usey maaf kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1308,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ne farmaya : ''maaldaar aadmi ka qarz ki adaegi mein taal matol karna zulm hai padhi. aur jab tum mein sey koi kisi maaldaar ki hawalgi mein diya jaaey to chaahiye ke uski hawalgi usey qubul karey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein ibne-Umar aur Shareed bin Suwed Saqafi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain.
1309,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maaldaar aadmi ka qarz ki adaegi mein taal matol karna zulm hai. aur jab tum kisi maaldaar key hawaley kiye jaao to usey qubul kar lo, aur eik bai (saude) mein do bai (saude) na karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is ka matlab ye hai ke jab tum mein sey koi qarz wasul karney mein kisi maaldaar key hawaley kiya jaey to usey qubul karna chahiye. 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab aadmi ko kisi maaldaar key hawaley kiya jaey aur wo hawala qubul kar ley to hawaley karney wala bari ho jaeyga aur qarz chahney key liye durust nahin ke phir hawaley karney waley ki taraf paltey. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : ke jis aadmi ki taraf tahweel (supurd) kiya gaya hai, key muflis ho janey ki wajeh sey uskey maal key doob janey ka khatra ho to qarz chahney key liye jayez hoga ke wo pehley ki taraf lot jaaey, un logon ney is baat par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) waghera key qol sey daleel di hai ke musalman ka maal zaya nahin hota hai. 5- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : is hadees (Ali maal Muslim tawi)''musalman ka maal zaya nahin hota hai''  ka matlab ye hai ke jab koi qarz chahney kisi key hawaley kiya gaya aur usey maaldaar samajh raha ho lekin dar-haqiqat wo gharib ho to aisi surat mein musalman ka maal zaya na hoga (aur wo asal qarz daar sey apna maal talab kar sakta hai)."
1310,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney munaabiza aur mulaamisa ke saude sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- is hadees ka matlab ye hai ke koi shakhs ye kahey : jab main tumhari taraf ye chiz phenk dun to merey aur tumharey darmiyan bai (sauda) wajib ho jaeygi (ye munaabiza ki surat hai). aur mulaamisa ye hai ke koi shakhs ye kahey : jab main ye chiz chhulun to bai (sauda) wajib ho jaeygi agar-che wo saman ko bilkul na dekh raha ho. maslan theley waghera mein ho. ye dono jahiliyat ke raaij saudon mein sey thin lihaza aap ney is sey mana farmaya.
1311,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madina tashrif laye aur ehale Madina phalon mein salaf kiya kartey they yani qeemat pehley ada kar detey they, aap ney farmaya : ''jo salaf karey wo mutayyan (tai-shuda) naap tol aur mutayyan (tai-shuda) muddat mein salaf karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi aur Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log ghalla , kapda , aur jin chizon ki had aur sift malum ho uski kharidari key liye peshgi raqam deney ko jayez kehtey hain. 4- janwer kharidney key liye peshgi raqam deney mein ikhtilaf hai. 5- baaz ehle-ilm janwer kharidney key liye peshgi raqam deney ko jayez kehtey hain. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney janwer kharidney key liye peshgi deney ko makrooh samjha hai. Sufiyan aur ehle-Koofa ka yehi qol hai."
1312,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis aadmi key baagh mein koi saajhi-daar ho to wo apna hissa us waqt tak na bechey jab tak ke usey apney saajhi-daar par pesh na kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad muttasil (lage hue) nahin hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Suleman (Alaihissalam) Yashkari key barey mein kaha jata hai ke wo Jabir bin Abdullah ki zindagi hi mein mar gaey they, un sey Qatada aur abu-Bashar ka samaa (sun'na), nahin hai. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : main nahin janta hun ke un mein sey kisi ney Suleman (Alaihissalam) Yashkari sey kuchh suna ho siwaye Amr bin Dinar key, shayad unhoney Jabir bin Abdullah ki zindagi hi mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) Yashkari sey hadees suni ho. wo kehtey hain ke Qatada , Suleman (Alaihissalam) Yashkari ki kitab sey hadees riwayat kartey they, Suleman (Alaihissalam) key paas eik kitab thi jis mein Jabir bin Abdullah sey marvi (riwayat hui) hadeesen likhi thin. 3- Suleman (Alaihissalam) Tameemi kehtey hain : log Jabir bin Abdullah ki kitab Hasan Basri key paas ley gaey to unhoney usey liya ya uski riwayat ki. aur log usey Qatada key paas ley gaey to unhoney bhi uski riwayat ki aur merey paas ley kar aaye to mainey uski riwayat nahin ki mainey usey radd kar diya."
1313,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bai (saude) muhaaqla , muzaabna padhi. , mukhaahira padhi. aur muaawma padhi. sey mana farmaya, aur aap ney araayaa (hadiye ke taur par di jane wali jins ko muzaabna ki shakl mein) ki ijazat di hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1314,"Eik baar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane mein (ghalla waghera ka ( bhaaw badh gaya, to logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap hamarey liye bhaaw muqarrar kar dijiye, aap ney farmaya : '' bhaaw muqarrar karney wala to Allah hi hai, wohi rozi tang karney wala , kushada karney wala aur kholney wala aur bahut rozi deney wala hai. main chahta hun ke apney rab sey us haal mein miloon ke tum mein sey koi mujh sey jaan aur maal key silsiley mein kisi zulm (key badley) ka mutalba karney wala na ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1315,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik ghalle key dher sey guzrey , to aap ney uskey andar apna haath dakhil kar diya, aap ki ungliyan tar ho gaeen to aap ney farmaya : ''ghalle waley ! ye kya maamla hai?'' usney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! barish sey bheeg gaya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''isey ooper kyon nahin kar diya taake log dekh saken.''  phir aap ney farmaya : ''jo dhoka dey, hum mein sey nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar, Abu Hamraa, ibne-Abbas , Barida , abu-Barda bin Dinar aur Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo dhoka-dhadi ko napasand kartey hain aur isey haram kehtey hain."
1316,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik jawan oont qarz liya aur aap ney isey is sey behtar oont diya aur farmaya : ''tum mein sey behtar wo log hain jo qarz ki adaegi mein behtar hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Shoba aur Sufiyan ney bhi Salma sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- is bab mein abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kisi bhi umr ka oont qarz leney ko makrooh nahin samajhtey hain. 5- aur baaz logon ney isey makrooh jana hai."
1317,"Eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (qarz ka ( taqaaza kiya aur sakhti ki, Sahaba ney isey dafa karney ka qasd (irada) (iraada) kiya to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''usey chhod do, kyonkey haqdaar ko kehney ka haq hai.''  phir aap ney farmaya : ''usey eik oont kharid kar dey do.''  logon ney talash kiya to unhen aisa hi oont mila jo uskey oont sey behtar tha, aap ney farmaya : ''isi ko kharid kar dey do, kyonkey tum mein behtar wo log hain jo qarz ki adaegi mein behtar hon.''"
1318,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik jawan oont qarz liya , phir aap key paas sadqey ka oont aaya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey hukm diya ke main us aadmi ka oont ada kar dun, mainey aap sey arz kiya : mujhey chaar daanton waley eik umda oont key ilawa koi aur oont nahin mil raha hai, to aap ney farmaya : ''isey usi ko dey do, kyonkey logon mein sab sey achchhey wo hain jo qarz ki adaegi mein sab sey achchhey hon.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1319,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala bechney , kharidney aur qarz key mutalbe mein narmi aur aasani ko pasand karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- baaz logon ney is hadees ko basanad « an Yonus an Saeed Al Maqbari an abi Huraira» riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1320,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney eik shakhs ko jo tum sey pehley tha bakhsh diya, jo narmi karney wala tha jab bechtaa aur jab khareedtaa aur jab qarz ka mutalba karta.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is tareeq sey Hasan , sahih , gharib hai."
1321,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum aisey shakhs ko dekho jo masjid mein kharid aur farokht kar raha ho to kaho : Allah Taala tumhari tijarat mein nafa na dey , aur jab aisey shakhs ko dekho jo masjid mein gumshuda chiz (ka aelan kartey huye usey) talash karta ho to kaho : Allah tumhari chiz tumhen na lotaye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo masjid mein kharid aur farokht najaaiz samajhtey hain. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney is mein kharid aur farokht ki rukhsat di hai."
